22 def call_service(service_name, service_msg_type, *args):
23  # Connect to service
24  rospy.wait_for_service(service_name, service_timeout)
25  # Call service
26  service = rospy.ServiceProxy(service_name, service_msg_type)
27  response = service(*args)
28  return response

57  def assertStatus(self, ret):
58  self.assertIsNotNone(ret, msg="Assert Status cannot operate on None ret")

147  @staticmethod
148  def save_workspace(name, list_poses_raw):
149  list_poses = []
150  for p in list_poses_raw:
151  point = Point(*p[0])
152  rpy = RPY(*p[1])
153  list_poses.append(RobotState(position=point, rpy=rpy, orientation=Quaternion()))
154  req = ManageWorkspaceRequest()
155  req.cmd = ManageWorkspaceRequest.SAVE
156  req.workspace.name = name
157  req.workspace.poses = list_poses
158  return call_service('/niryo_robot_poses_handlers/manage_workspace', ManageWorkspace, req)
159 
160  @staticmethod
161  def save_workspace_from_points(name, list_points_raw):
162  list_points = []
163  for p in list_points_raw:
164  list_points.append(Point(*p))
165  req = ManageWorkspaceRequest()
166  req.cmd = ManageWorkspaceRequest.SAVE_WITH_POINTS
167  req.workspace.name = name
168  req.workspace.points = list_points
169  return call_service('/niryo_robot_poses_handlers/manage_workspace', ManageWorkspace, req)
